      S is a good semigroup. Determines the Arf good semigroup closure of S.


gap> G:=[[3,3],[4,4],[5,4],[4,6]];
[ [ 3, 3 ], [ 4, 4 ], [ 5, 4 ], [ 4, 6 ] ]
